##Tools & Commands Used
Tool	                            Purpose                                                     	Sample Commands / Usage
Burp Suite	                 API interception, token analysis, manual authorization testing 	Proxy Intercept, Repeater, Intruder
Postman	                     API request crafting, GraphQL query fuzzing	                    Custom GET/POST requests
sqlmap                       Automated injection detection & validation                      	sqlmap -u http://target/api/users?id=1 --risk=3 --level=5
Nmap	                       API service discovery	                                          nmap -p 80,443 target
Linux                        CLI	Manual API testing & logging	                              curl, grep, cat
